      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">225.7204</ph> Solicitation provision and contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Except for acquisitions described in 
               <xref base="DFARS-225.7202"
                  href="225.7202.dita#DFARS_225.7202"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">225.7202</xref>
            —</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="List1"> (a) Use the provision at <xref href="https://www.acq.osd.mil/dpap/dars/dfars/html/current/252225.htm#252.225-7003"
                  format="html"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">252.225-7003</xref>, Report of Intended Performance Outside the United States and Canada—Submission with Offer, in solicitations with a value exceeding $20 million; and</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="List1"> (b) Use the clause at <xref href="https://www.acq.osd.mil/dpap/dars/dfars/html/current/252225.htm#252.225-7004"
                  format="html"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">252.225-7004</xref>, Report of Intended Performance Outside the United States and Canada—Submission after Award, in solicitations and contracts with a value exceeding $20 million.</p>
